# ── Build artifacts & caches ───────────────────────────────────
# Use **/ prefix so nested directories are also excluded (e.g. builder/node_modules/)
# Critical: without this, COPY builder/ . would overwrite the Alpine-native
# binaries (esbuild, sharp, etc.) with glibc binaries from the host, crashing the build.
**/node_modules/
dist/
builder/dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Source (compiled in Dockerfile Stage 1) ────────────────────
# src/ is COPIED explicitly in the build stage; exclude from context
# to avoid double-sending. tsconfig.json is also copied explicitly.
# NOTE: Do NOT ignore src/ or tsconfig.json — they are needed by the builder stage.

# ── Planning / docs (not needed in image) ─────────────────────
# License & attribution texts MUST reach the build context so the runtime image
# can ship them (see the Dockerfile runner stage). LICENSE has no extension so
# *.md never matched it, but the negations are kept explicit and defensive.
*.md
!README.md
!LICENSE
!THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md

# ── OS / editor junk ──────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Archives ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
